sits down with senior Trump
adviser Kellyanne

00:26.159 --> 00:28.829 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
Conway to look at the
president's first week
in office.

00:28.862 --> 00:33.133 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And aging out of
the middle
class, the second part of our
look at the

00:33.166 --> 00:37.571 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
