Minister Theresa
May is talking up cooperation
with the new

07:43.530 --> 07:48.368 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Trump administration on her
first visit to
the U.S. as prime minister.

07:48.401 --> 07:53.773 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
