to leave
the European Union.

07:57.444 --> 08:01.614 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
THERESA MAY, British Prime
Minister: As we
rediscover our confidence
together, as you

08:01.648 --> 08:10.123 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
renew your nation, just as we
renew ours,
we have the opportunity, indeed
the responsibility,

08:10.156 --> 08:14.127 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
