together again.

08:17.330 --> 08:21.634 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: May is set to
meet with President
Trump at the White House
tomorrow.

08:21.668 --> 08:26.106 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
ANTONIO MORA: Cheers erupted in
the West African
nation of Gambia today as the
new president

08:26.139 --> 08:29.209 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
