president in
two decades.

08:43.523 --> 08:46.659 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
He's promised to reverse
Jammeh's authoritarian
policies.

08:46.693 --> 08:51.398 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: In Australia,
celebrations
and protests competed as the
country marked

08:51.431 --> 08:53.199 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Australia Day.

08:53.233 --> 08:59.205 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
