difficulties.

36:03.495 --> 36:08.299 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: Now Gabler, like
Elizabeth White,
readily admits he could have
saved more, been

36:08.333 --> 36:11.836 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
more frugal, but so could a lot
of us.

36:11.870 --> 36:20.378 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
In 2015, fully 46 percent of
adults said they'd
have to borrow or pawn to come
