38:44.355 --> 38:45.323 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
WOMAN: Forever.

38:45.356 --> 38:46.324 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
WOMAN: For forever.

38:46.357 --> 38:47.525 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
FLORIE LISER: I mean, I just
