39:09.981 --> 39:11.683 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
PAUL SOLMAN: The smugtocracy.

39:11.716 --> 39:13.518 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ELIZABETH WHITE: Smugtocracy.

39:13.551 --> 39:18.489 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
