relocate.

40:37.201 --> 40:40.238 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
CASEY AFFLECK: Relocate to
where?

40:40.271 --> 40:42.040 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
Here?

40:42.073 --> 40:46.277 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: As played by
Casey Affleck,
Lee is a lost, mostly silent man
at sea over

40:46.311 --> 40:47.745 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
