couldn't write or
direct a movie if you weren't
able to do that.

41:53.778 --> 41:55.446 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And how do you do
that?

41:55.480 --> 41:57.515 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
KENNETH LONERGAN: When it's
going well, you
don't have to think these things
through.

41:57.548 --> 41:59.350 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
