in the room
with him.

42:01.419 --> 42:04.689 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
And I -- then they start
talking, and I write
it down.

42:04.722 --> 42:09.093 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And when it's not going well, I
try to get
back to that place.

42:09.127 --> 42:15.166 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: But are you
writing the pauses,
the shuffles, the -- you know,
the moments

42:15.199 --> 42:17.201 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
