42:57.675 --> 43:04.215 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: With
"Manchester," Lonergan
again deals with loss and the
whole idea of

43:04.248 --> 43:06.083 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
