53:13.390 --> 53:14.358 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MAN: My name is Miguel (ph).

53:14.391 --> 53:15.459 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MAN: My names is Charles Spence
(ph).

53:15.492 --> 53:16.994 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
MAN: My name is Newton Pangthong
(ph).

53:17.027 --> 53:21.265 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN: My name is Mike, and this
is my Brief
But Spectacular take.

53:21.298 --> 53:23.133 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
MAN: Brief But Spectacular take.

53:23.167 --> 53:27.671 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
MAN: This is my Brief But
Spectacular take
on doing time.

